wiki.summary: On “Calling My Phone,“ Lil Tjay and 6LACK both croon about the difficulties of moving on from their respective past relationships. Tjay previewed the track numerous times on Twitter and TikTok in December 2020 and January 2021. The song’s feature was speculated numerous times and later confirmed through a tweet on February 8. However, the track’s release date was revealed through a phone call that was recorded on February 4.
